      "content": "**Step-by-Step Resolution:**\n1. **22:12 UTC**: Added ephemeral port outbound rule (1024-65535) to NACL\n2. **22:28 UTC**: Changed INBOUND Rule 101 from \"HTTPS (443)\" to \"All Traffic\"\n3. **23:08 UTC**: ",
